      "parts": [{
        "text": "**Designing the App**\n\nI\u0027m focusing on the app\u0027s initial design for a preschooler, emphasizing simplicity, vibrant colors, engaging sounds, and game mechanics. My current priority is to make the content in English but translate the instructions into Portuguese, creating an interactive learning experience.\n\n\n",
        "thought": true
